Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:41.70,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「死不过是解脱」我的朋友曾这样对我说。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:45.70,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,La mort n'est jamais qu'un salut,ainsi mon ami a t'il murmurer jadis amon intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.60,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「若死是解脱，那你究竟想带给他们什么呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:50.60,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,asupposer que la mort soit un salut,que veux tu donner quand atoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:49.90,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友只回答了一句话。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:51.90,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,mon ami arépondu en un souffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:54.00,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我要给他们永远的痛苦与悔恨…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:57.00,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,Chez eux une souffrance et un remord éternel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我不会再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十二幕\N反击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的选择真的是正确吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就没什么真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓真理是在自己的信念之下创造出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使同室操戈 甚至抛弃父母也在所不惜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不能光看父母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而要看眼前的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在弗朗兹死去的前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我听了您的告白后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就一直走到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着波光粼漓的河流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪就止不住地涌了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我还清楚地记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹给我留下了几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「绝对不要恨任何人」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「爱人的心情和恨人的心情」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「最初都是由思念之情中产生的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切都告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为爱德蒙最后的单身之夜干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受莫尔塞夫将军之命前来迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军即将进入巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将建立临时政府
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天之内莫尔塞夫大统领即将诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请带我去 到他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…费尔南·蒙代戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民议会被我们东方宇宙军占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是重大的叛逆行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承认 决不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…真无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您慎重发言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在解散原议会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣布巴黎进入戒严状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个名叫爱德蒙·唐泰斯的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 直到那天我还对人毫无戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心祈祷着父亲与未婚妻的幸福 渡过每日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现将你作为暗杀王子案的重大嫌疑人逮捕归案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙 爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被告发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人告密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据那封告发信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你持有记载暗杀王子案真相的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长去世前 应该交托给你一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按照船长的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备把信送到收件人那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巴黎 鸡鹭街13号」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「诺瓦蒂埃先生」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信中写有与暗杀王子案有关的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中也包括维尔福的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不知情的我将信交给了当事人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你只是出色地完成了任务而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐泰斯先生 关于此信的事就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就会被释放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 维尔福先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知该如何感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚妻一定正焦急地等着我回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这封信的事你和别人说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 根据船长的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直坚守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道这封信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到现在还相信王子是被敌人暗杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是地球方面的设计
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战争中牟取暴利的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望战争继续
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暗杀为最坏结局收场 和平无望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中他们下怀 纷争扩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暗杀的报复为名 战争愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然…然后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个不幸的男人…被埋葬于黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用了我的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在经济司法等界各自崭露头角
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在军事界爬到顶峰的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终向大统领的地位进发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫维尔福先生来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底犯了什么罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没做 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆在被收监入伊夫堡的我面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无尽的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了对付边境外未知敌人的自动化要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也成了那控制系统的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 甚至连死亡的选择也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无限的地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不期望救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这身体消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那些夺去我一切 把我逼向毁灭的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都受到最残酷 最悲惨的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要给他们生不如死 永无止境的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.80,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.80,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.70,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.70,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.60,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.60,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.40,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.40,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}l'espoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.40,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.40,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le chagrin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.80,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.80,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le désir ardent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.40,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.40,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la résignation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.90,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.90,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la colère...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.40,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.40,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la terreur...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.20,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.20,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le désespoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.70,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再一次希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.70,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}et anouveau l'espoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.00,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等待着像你这样的人的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.00,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}cela fait des milliers d'années que j'attendais
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.50,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了借用这个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:51.50,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}al'intérieur de ce coprs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.00,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数千年间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.00,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la venue de quelqu'un
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.80,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等待着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.80,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}comme...toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:02.30,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.10,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.10,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Je suis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.40,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将与你同在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.40,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}avec toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.60,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.60,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Et tu es
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.70,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也与我同在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.70,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}avec moi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:16.70,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借给你我的智慧和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:16.70,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Je te donne ma sagesse et mon pouvoir
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.20,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.20,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}et toi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:21.50,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要献出你的身体与心灵…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:21.50,*notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}tu m'offres ton esprit et ton corps...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 我是命运的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不过是这坚定的复仇之心在驱动着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是不希望您去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您打消这个念头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够命令基督山伯爵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有基督山伯爵一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的心中 难道已经…没有任何人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所认识的伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道已经…已经消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙军正向大学等机关移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请市民们尽快避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙军正向大学等机关移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请市民们尽快避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的金子 我的金子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间不过如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死刑 死刑 死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 别阻拦我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别关机哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对伯爵要保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器储藏库
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我不知道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们见识一下我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯旋门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无能之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 巴黎终于被我征服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不应该是你所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我说的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满溢着更多希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 这是国民所必需的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是大统领夫人了 梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无所畏惧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙就活在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是你的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是我未婚夫的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以基督山伯爵的身份回到了我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了复仇而回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇？你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和爱德蒙不是好友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么爱德蒙一定要向你复仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他…是好友…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不认为那家伙是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你的漂亮话有多伤人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄出让他被捕的信的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将会是钢铁之舰法老号的船长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我只是个马塞港的苦力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…是你的漂亮话让爱德蒙坠入不幸的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我对你说了多么过分的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开巴黎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经厌烦那种丧家犬般的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够只能望其项背的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要留在这
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留在 我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记和你度过的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 费尔南
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深爱着她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我爱你…胜过一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙代戈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那家伙还活着 我也不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你对我做的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要夺走你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将继续祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为父亲 为母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有为最重要的您之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 岩窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三幕\N爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然后期待
